00:08:49,460 --> 00:08:53,330
Apa kalian ke sini untuk pesta perpisahan Nicchi juga?

119
00:08:53,900 --> 00:08:55,169
Nicchi?

120
00:08:55,170 --> 00:08:56,749
Pesta perpisahan?

121
00:08:56,750 --> 00:08:58,470
Apa yang kau bicarakan?

122
00:08:58,650 --> 00:09:01,350
