154
00:10:41,320 --> 00:10:44,379
Lagipula, Nichihara Taisei...

155
00:10:44,380 --> 00:10:46,580
Adalah pria yang kami sebutkan tadi, Nicchi.

156
00:10:46,810 --> 00:10:51,530
Pria yang bunuh diri di sini dua bulan lalu.

157
00:10:52,260 --> 00:10:54,090
Apa?

